draw_text(info1_x, info1_y, "Katyusha is a Soviet folk-based song and military march.\nCreated in 1938, this song by Matvey Blanter gained fame\nduring World War II as a patriotic song which inspired\nthe comrades to serve and defend their motherland. The song\nis about a Russian woman called Katyusha. Standing on a\nsteep riverbank, she sends her song to her lover, a soldier\nserving far away who will protect the Motherland and its\npeople.");